Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.57,0:24:20.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c48] I wonder if even God will be astonished! {神様もびっくり仰天かなって！ kami-sama mo bikkuri gyouten kanatte! }
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.97,0:24:20.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c94] Is the fighting... going to end? {戦いが…終わるのか… tatakai ga... owaru noka...}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.91,0:24:22.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c51] At this rate, it seems like nobody would even notice if I was gone! {このままいなくなっても、誰も気づかなそうだからなぁ！ konomama inakuna tte mo, daremo kizukana souda kara na !}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.32,0:24:21.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c116] Disappear! {消えろっ！ kiero-!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.51,0:24:21.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:22.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c7] Wretchedly disappear like toilet paper! {トイレットペーパーのように惨めに消えろ！ toirette peepaa no youni mijime ni kiero !}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:22.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c44] I only act when it will assist Yurippe! {俺が動くのはゆりっぺの助けになるときだけだ！ ore ga ugoku no wa yurippe no tasuke ni naru toki dake da!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c81] Think of it as though your combat potential has raised by... 100 men. {百人…、戦力が増えたと思え  hyakunin... senryoku ga fueta to omoe}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c26] Let's form a band again next time! {次もバンドやるよ！ tsugi mo bando yaru yo!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:25.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c217] So you finally made it this far, huh? {よく辿り着けましたね yoku tadori tsukemashite ne}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.64,0:24:25.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c174] Give me your hand! {手を伸ばせ!  te o nobase !}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.56,0:24:28.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c157] If we disappear from here... can we try it all again? {ここから消えたら, ...やり直せますかね koko kara kietera, ...yarinaosemasu ka ne}
